        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2010-03-12T15:16:48Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Honest and Open Testimony Act - Includes within communications by a member of the Armed Forces that are protected from retaliatory personnel actions any testimony provided in a congressional hearing regarding the disclosure of sexual orientation, including that the member is homosexual, bisexual, or transgender.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
